## Initialize backend project (Node.js + TypeScript + Express)
## 1 add nod.js
mkdir services
cd services
pnpm init 

## 2 add exprees
pnpm add express dotenv
pnpm add -D typescript ts-node nodemon @types/node @types/express
## 3 add tcpescript
npx tsc --init 
or from root project pnpm add express --filter @relay/hello-service

add to user sevice
pnpm add express --filter @relay/users

# run server  semple service backend

pnpm turbo run dev --filter=@relay/hello-service


Users Service running on port 3003
hello Service running on port 3002


